snippet.title: Stand and Fight - Stage 1 & 2
snippet.description:
Stand & Fight is a game about looking for the past to understand where your strength comes from, and fight back against those who try to push you down for who you are.

Developed in a month and a half, Stand and Fight was nominated as one of the winners of the Quick Play 2022 Game Jam, and it is available on the Play Store for free!
